{"tid":1519333,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"End game只係phase 4既開始！","createTime":"2019-08-30T14:10:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T14:29:29.000Z","uid":198684,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e3f59696ee40045c560ccbcfde61056294cec68a","tid":1519333,"uid":198684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T14:10:41.000Z","msg":"由今日下晝開始就一個接一個既post話聽日係end game。 但大家記住 end game並唔係終點！相反係phase 4既起點！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n與其講係終點，不如講會係一個轉捩點，30/8 對方突然急速拘捕曝光既眾人，無論佢地係想殺雞儆猴或白色恐佈，對方都開始轉玩法，佢哋都開始急了因為臨近1/10。<br />\n而我地都會同需要隨住轉我地既抗爭方法！唔好忘記三個月黎有幾多義士犧牲！被捕！時代巨輪一直會轉，永遠唔會有end game一日，因為即使勝利，我地都要建造一個美好既香港！抗爭之路從來唔短，故事會一直寫落去！ 但之後「香港」既故事係點，就靠「香港人」齊心去寫！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可<br />\n勿忘義士<br />\n香港人加油<br />\n終點也是起點</span></span>"},{"pid":"0b1a6c27b6e87714c0cef75730f1425bb8f8eccd","tid":1519333,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T14:11:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qw3QgZA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQw3QgZA.jpg&h=c3ca146d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0h%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=8eb4f3a2\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=7hy